      <th scope=\"col\" data-row=\"0\" data-col=\"1\"> </th>\n                <th scope=\"col\" data-row=\"0\" data-col=\"2\">Wage</th>\n                <th scope=\"col\" data-row=\"0\" data-col=\"3\">Log Wage</th>\n              </tr>\n        </thead>\n        \n        <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"1\" data-col=\"1\">(Intercept)</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"1\" data-col=\"2\">-276.240</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"1\" data-col=\"3\">5.497</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"2\" data-col=\"1\"></td>\n                  <td data-row=\"2\" data-col=\"2\">(108.828)</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"2\" data-col=\"3\">(0.112)</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"3\" data-col=\"1\">educ</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"3\" data-col=\"2\">74.415</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"3\" data-col=\"3\">0.075</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"4\" data-col=\"1\"></td>\n                  <td data-row=\"4\" data-col=\"2\">(6.745)</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"4\" data-col=\"3\">(0.007)</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"5\" data-col=\"1\">exper</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"5\" data-col=\"2\">14.892</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"5\" data-col=\"3\">0.015</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"6\" data-col=\"1\"></td>\n                  <td data-row=\"6\" data-col=\"2\">(3.246)</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"6\" data-col=\"3\">(0.003)</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"7\" data-col=\"1\">tenure</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"7\" data-col=\"2\">8.257</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"7\" data-col=\"3\">0.013</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"8\" data-col=\"1\"></td>\n                  <td data-row=\"8\" data-col=\"2\">(2.504)</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"8\" data-col=\"3\">(0.003)</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"9\" data-col=\"1\">Num.Obs.</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"9\" data-col=\"2\">935</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"9\" data-col=\"3\">935</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td data-row=\"10\" data-col=\"1\">R2</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"10\" data-col=\"2\">0.146</td>\n                  <td data-row=\"10\" data-col=\"3\">0.155</td>\n                </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n<!-- hack to avoid NA insertion in last line -->\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.callout-note title=\"Questions\"}\n1. Come si interpretano i coefficients di $educ$ nelle due regressioni?\n2. I coefficients sono statisticamente significativi al 5%? (Calcolare anche l'intervallo di confidenza al 95%)\n3. Wald test (statistica F robusta all'heteroskedasticity) che tutti i coefficients della regressione siano uguali a zero\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n### Istruzione dei genitori: dataset `wage2`\n\nUsiamo il dataset `wage2` considerando $pareduc$ che rappresenta la somma degli years of education dei genitori. $wage$ in `wage2` è il wage espresso in dollari mensili:\n\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nwage2 <- wage2 %>%\n  mutate(pareduc = meduc + feduc)\n```\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nregeduc_int <- feols(wage ~ educ*pareduc + exper + tenure, data = wage2, vcov = \"hetero\")\nregeduc_intlog <- feols(log(wage) ~ educ*pareduc + exper + tenure, data = wage2, vcov = \"hetero\")\nmodelsummary(list(\"Wage \" = regeduc_int, \"Log Wage \" = regeduc_intlog), gof_omit = \"AIC|BIC|RMSE|R2 Adj.\")\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- preamble start -->\n\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/vincentarelbun